&lt;p&gt;This is a role for someone who wants to run the whole business. We’re looking for a Chief Commercial Officer, GTM to own the full commercial motion across North America — new logo acquisition, account expansion, renewals, and the operational infrastructure that makes it all run. Our clients are institutional — asset managers, allocators, wealth platforms, hedge funds — and they expect a different level of engagement than a typical Enterprise B2B transaction. Relationships are long, deals are complex, and retention is earned every year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll inherit a team of ~15 and a mandate to grow it and you will report to the Chief Revenue Officer (CRO). Your job is to assess what’s working, rebuild what isn’t, and install the discipline and culture that scales.&lt;/p&gt;
