&lt;li&gt;Commercial revenue accountability for North America — you are accountable for the full revenue line, and for ensuring that deals are structured to be margin-accretive to Rimes and that the commercial motion generates returns consistent with the firm’s growth thesis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
